EXAMPLE(S): A request for approval to either market a product or to allow the applicant to start testing of a proposed product. NOTE(S): In most cases, the compilation of the submission units is used to assess a product's quality, safety and effectiveness. Submissions are always associated with some regulatory action (or inaction). Each submission contains their own regulatory action. Submissions (e.g., initial marketing application, supplemental marketing application) would generally be comprised of multiple submissions units.
